-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/T%E1%BA%A1-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-t%E1%BB%95ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-Kh%E1%BB%95ng-c%C3%B4ng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-G2tpt59CWHsnu6SB1WllHA">Tạ Lưỡng Quảng tổng đốc Khổng công kỳ 1 - 謝兩廣總督孔公其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/author-Kf5yfK5iK_BR3H2g75GaXQ">Phạm Khiêm Ích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C6%B0-s%C3%A0o-k%C3%BD/poem-so9_x8JRDS-uH2_aEO4INA">Thư sào ký - 書巢記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Kh%C3%A1nh-Ninh-ki%E1%BB%81u/poem-3HbVDCUDnTeZnqsF2xlbBw">Vịnh Khánh Ninh kiều - 詠慶寧橋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i/poem-VsuzLp95JE0OMWqtrvsVCA">Xuân nhật cảm hoài - 春日感懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
